bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "r2d2wm-bot"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "r2d2wm-bot"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = ["No√© Ksiazek <noe@ksiazek.xyz>"]
rust-version = "1.79"

[dependencies]
async-std = "1.12.0"
async-trait = "0.1.80"
chrono = "0.4.38"
chrono-tz = "0.9.0"
dotenvy = "0.15.7"
serde_json = "1.0.118"
serenity = "0.12.2"
thiserror = "1.0.61"
tokio-cron-scheduler = "0.10.2"
tracing = "0.1.40"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.203"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.38.0"
features = ["macros", "rt-multi-thread"]

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3.18"
features = ["env-filter"]

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1.9.0"
features = ["v4"]

[dev-dependencies]
serde_test = "1.0.176"
